import React from 'react'
import SectionHeader from './SectionHeader'
import CaseStudyCard from './CaseStudyCard'
import TomoImage from '../Assets/case-study-placeholder.png'
import CaseStudyArchived from './CaseStudyArchived'

export default function RecentWork() {
    return (
        <section className="section-container">

            <SectionHeader description="02 / 05 | RECENT WORK" title="What I've been up to recently" />

            <CaseStudyArchived
                projectName = "Kairos"
                projectDescription = "Find your moment"
                link = "https://www.trykairos.com"
            />
            
            <CaseStudyCard
                projectName = "Katch"
                projectDescription = "Flexible meetings with real time availability"
                projectScope = "UI/UX Designer at Katch"
                projectPlatforms = "iOS, Slack"
                projectTimeline = "10/22 - 11/22"
                projectImage={TomoImage}
            />

            <CaseStudyCard
                projectName = "Sismo"
                projectDescription = "The key primitive for Web3 identities"
                projectScope = "Collaborative design exercise"
                projectPlatforms = "Web app"
                projectTimeline = "12/22"
                projectImage={TomoImage}
            />

            <CaseStudyCard
                projectName = "Tomo"
                projectDescription = "Time management made easiest."
                projectScope = "Solo, conceptual"
                projectPlatforms = "Android"
                projectTimeline = "04/22 - 06/22"
                projectImage={TomoImage}
            />

            <CaseStudyArchived
                projectName = "Focusmate"
                projectDescription = "Virtual coworking for getting anything done"
                link = "https://www.trykairos.com"
            />

            <CaseStudyArchived
                projectName = "Paro"
                projectDescription = "Your home renovation advisors"
                link = "https://www.trykairos.com"
            />

            <CaseStudyArchived
                projectName = "VidBib"
                projectDescription = "A new hiring economy"
                link = "https://www.trykairos.com"
            />



        </section>
    )
}
